title: time management, deciding to go back to school + application tips

description:
Brooke and Danielle are joined by Kiara Madisen!  The gals discuss going to nursing school, having a traditional undergrad experience and how Kiara manages her multifaceted life.  Kiara shares some tips to fellow students and discusses how she organizes her life, her application process to nursing school and her Certified Nursing Assistant License.
